2014-03-24	daniffig	<daniffig@gmail.com>

	* Starting Model, Views and Controllers build.
	
	* Quizzes can be added using plain text files. UTF-8 encoding is required to display everything OK.
	
	* Questions can be navigated using the top spinner or the bottom actions 'Previous' and 'Next'.	
	
	* Answers can be checked using the action 'Check'.
	
	* Questions and Answers are displayed randomly.